sequenceDiagram
accTitle: Mermaid rect highlighting
accDescr {
Demonstrates Mermaid rect highlighting mapped onto sequencer fragments with inferred actor spans.
From the project root, regenerate this Mermaid transform and SVG with:
node sequencer.js --mermaid -i test/mermaid-features/14-rect-highlighting/input.mmd -o -f -t test/mermaid-features/14-rect-highlighting
}
participant Caller
participant Service
participant DB
participant Cache
Caller->>Service: Start request [Mermaid: Caller->>Service: Start request]
rect rgba(255, 220, 180, 0.5)
  Service->>DB: Persist record [Mermaid: Service->>DB: Persist record]
  DB-->>Service: Persistence complete [Mermaid: DB-->>Service: Persistence complete]
end
rect rgb(210, 240, 255)
  Service->>Cache: Warm cache [Mermaid: Service->>Cache: Warm cache]
  Note over Service,Cache: Highlighted cache phase [Mermaid: Note over Service,Cache: Highlighted cache phase]
end
Service-->>Caller: Reply [Mermaid: Service-->>Caller: Reply]
